snippet.title: Zombie Blast Crew | Blast Crew update
snippet.description:
Free on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/zombie-blast-crew/id1455256869
Get it on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vividgames.modernpioneer

They're finally here: the first Blast Crew members have deployed. The survivors each come with their own stats, skills, unique weapon and playstyle. War veteran Michael and his assault rifle will be your first member, with four more to unlock - for now.
Also new: more polished animations (shooting, reloading, running), as well as different weathers (night, sunny, overcast...).
